        <mxCell id="p5-p2-clibox" parent="p5-1" style="rounded=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFFDE7,#2a2a14);strokeColor=#F9A825;strokeWidth=2;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=10;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=light-dark(#BF5700,#FFD180);spacing=8;fontStyle=1;whiteSpace=wrap;" value="CLI-side: `bgagent watch --transport auto &lt;task_id&gt;`&#xa;• 1. GET /tasks/{task_id} → snapshot.execution_mode&#xa;• 2. If execution_mode ≠ &#39;interactive&#39; (it&#39;s &#39;orchestrator&#39; here) → SKIP SSE attempt, go straight to polling (no 424 reconnect storm).&#xa;• 3. Poll: loop GET /tasks/{task_id}/events?after=&lt;last_event_id&gt; every ~500ms.&#xa;• 4. Exit on RUN_FINISHED / RUN_ERROR terminal event." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="120" width="1520" x="40" y="2070" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p5-p2-m9" edge="1" parent="p5-1" style="endArrow=classic;html=1;fontSize=10;fontFamily=Helvetica;labelBackgroundColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#8C4FFF;" value="9. GET /tasks/{id} → TaskDetail {execution_mode:&#39;orchestrator&#39;, status, ...}">
