        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p5clibox" parent="1" style="rounded=1;fillColor=light-dark(#FFFDE7,#2a2a14);strokeColor=#F9A825;strokeWidth=2;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=light-dark(#BF5700,#FFD180);spacing=10;fontStyle=1;whiteSpace=wrap;" value="Watch client decision logic — `bgagent watch &lt;task_id&gt; --transport auto`&#xa;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight:normal;font-size:10px&quot;&gt;1. GET /tasks/{id} → snapshot.execution_mode&lt;br&gt;2. If execution_mode ≠ &#39;interactive&#39; → skip SSE entirely (no 424 reconnect storm)&lt;br&gt;3. Poll GET /tasks/{id}/events?after=&lt;last_event_id&gt; every ~500ms (adaptive decay)&lt;br&gt;4. Render each event; exit 0 on RUN_FINISHED, exit 1 on RUN_ERROR&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
